[{"Id": 1013044, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Aqeel and Jafar-e-Tayyar, both are the brothers of Hazrat Ali (a). Abdullah bin Jafar Tayyar was the husband of Lady Zainab. The graves of these two personalities are in Baqi. Recite the Ziyarat of these noble personages in the following words…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Aqeel aur Jafar-e-Tayyar dono Hazrat Ali (a) ke bhai hai. Abdullah bin Jafar Tayyar, Bibi Zainab (s) ke shohar thay. In do buzurg hasti ki qabr Baqi mein hai. In do hazraat ki ziyarat is tarah se hai…", "UrduDescription": "جناب عقیل اور جناب جعفر طیّار دونوں حضرت علی ابن ابی طالبؑ کے بھائی ہیں۔ جعفر طیّار کے فرزند جناب عبد اللہ جناب زینبؑ کے شوہر ہیں۔ جناب عقیل اور جناب عبداللہ بن جعفر کی قبریں جنت البقیع میں ہیں۔ ان دونوں حضرات کی زیارت اس طرح پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11"